[COLOR=#e64a19][SIZE=4][B]Network Updates[/B][/SIZE][/COLOR]
This month, we did something special for Valentine's day -- we allowed you to send XP to each other for the first time, as a gift of a Valentine. Over the course of the 2-day event, 73,092 Valentines were sent out by Shotbow players. We also had some exclusive Valentine's cosmetics. Read our reflection on this month's event [URL='https://shotbow.net/forum/threads/valentine-statistics.383851/']here[/URL].

